DateTime::Locale::am(3) User Contributed Perl Documentation DateTime::Locale::am(3)

NAME

DateTime::Locale::am - Locale data examples for the Amharic (am) locale

DESCRIPTION

This pod file contains examples of the locale data available for the Amharic locale.

Date Formats

Full 

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 2008 ፌብሩወሪ 5, ማክሰኞ
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 1995 ዲሴምበር 22, ዓርብ
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = -10 ሴፕቴምበር 15, ቅዳሜ

Long

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 ፌብሩወሪ 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22 ዲሴምበር 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15 ሴፕቴምበር -10

Medium

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 ፌብሩ 2008

  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15 ሴፕቴ -10

Short

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 05/02/2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22/12/1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15/09/-10
